These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
City: paris, liverpool
There 2 different types of food: lime, peas
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person eating peas##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | iced-tea  |
| City       | liverpool    | paris    |
| Food   | peas       | lime      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, blues
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, fonseca
House: modern, farmhouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the modern house is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the modern house is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Music-Genre      | blues     | jazz |
| Cigar           | havana | fonseca      |
| House   | farmhouse  | modern      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, vegafina
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower
1. the fan of country is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the ranch-style house is the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| House      | ranch-style | gothic-revival  |
| Cigar          | swisher    | vegafina   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Flower     | bellflower     | amaryllis |

