The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, train
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
