.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
House: colonial, modern
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola
City: edinburgh, miami
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the colonial house is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the colonial house is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| House           | modern | colonial     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea          | cola |
| City           | edinburgh          | miami    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 